OL,5, The sister of a black man who died in  
OL,6, police custody received racist and     
OL,7, abusive messages during the public     
OL,8, inquiry into his death, a new BBC      
OL,9, programme can reveal.                  
OL,11,FKadi Johnson encountered the abuse     
OL,12,Fafter she told the inquiry into the    
OL,13,Fdeath of her brother, Sheku Bayoh, that
OL,14,Fshe no longer felt safe in Scotland.   
OL,16,FMr Bayoh died after being restrained on
OL,17,Fthe ground by six police officers.     
OL,19,FThe inquiry is investigating the       
OL,20,Fcircumstances of his death in 2015.    
